      "content": [
        {
          "type": "card",
          "variant": "simple",
          "title": {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "Chat Auto-translation: Real-time Traffic Handling and Asynchronous LLM Architecture"
          },
          "highlights": [
            "Real-time traffic handling",
            "Asynchronous LLM architecture",
            "Service stability",
            "Improved user experience"
          ],
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "card",
              "subtitle": "Context",
              "variant": "timeline",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "As users across different language groups increased, an automatic chat translation feature became necessary."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Chat is latency-sensitive, so translation quality, response speed, and stability all had to be satisfied together."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "An asynchronously separated architecture was needed to reduce LLM call bottlenecks."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "card",
              "subtitle": "Contribution",
              "variant": "timeline",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Separated the message pipeline from translation processing to minimize impact on chat UX."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Applied queue-and-worker processing to LLM translation requests to stabilize throughput during traffic spikes."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Designed retries/fallbacks for failure or latency and added bottleneck observability points."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Reviewed performance-quality trade-offs on production traffic and established an operational model that scales."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "card",
              "subtitle": "Outcome",
              "variant": "timeline",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Integrated LLM translation into the service flow while preserving real-time chat UX."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Established asynchronous patterns that reduce impact on the main chat path even during traffic fluctuations."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "card",
          "variant": "simple",
          "title": {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "Semantic Caching: 25% Annual LLM Cost Reduction via Vector Search"
          },
          "highlights": [
            "Intern-led proposal",
            "Real-time vector search",
            "Embedded vector DB usage"
          ],
          "link": {
            "text": "Read post",
            "url": "https://medium.com/p/af3de9a74d0c"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "card",
              "subtitle": "Context",
              "variant": "timeline",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "We introduced a feature that recommends chat utterances using LLMs to improve user experience."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "However, frequent LLM calls projected annual costs of around KRW 900 million."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "We needed a way to reduce cost while maintaining a similar user experience."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "card",
              "variant": "timeline",
              "subtitle": "Contribution",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Although I was an intern in another team at the time, I proactively proposed semantic caching with real-time vector search."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Embedded real chat data and identified semantic conversation clusters with PCA and HDBSCAN."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Used an add-on architecture separated from the main server and an embedded vector DB to prevent external traffic transfer."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Validated network I/O bottlenecks with load tests and handled concurrency with lightweight multi-replica deployment."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "card",
              "subtitle": "Outcome",
              "variant": "timeline",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Applied semantic caching to 13 frequently occurring utterance-semantic clusters in chat."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Achieved a 25% reduction in annual LLM call cost, saving over KRW 230 million."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "card",
          "variant": "simple",
          "title": {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "SHAP-based Interpretability PoC for Churn Probability Prediction by Chat Timestep"
          },
          "highlights": [
            "Integrated language + behavioral signals",
            "SHAP-based interpretability",
            "Response strategy discovery based on churn probability"
          ],
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "card",
              "subtitle": "Context",
              "variant": "timeline",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Chat data is time-series interaction data that densely reflects user experience issues."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "A text-only signal model made it difficult to clearly explain churn timing and causes."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "We ran a PoC enabling timestep-level churn probability estimation and SHAP-based cause interpretation."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "card",
              "variant": "timeline",
              "subtitle": "Contribution",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Structured BERT/DistilBERT embeddings plus sentiment, politeness, and closure-intent signals as core features."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Built a time-series feature pipeline combining response-time, message-length, and response-presence metadata."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Adopted a LightGBM-based model to reduce inference time while ensuring interpretability."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Performed SHAP-based feature contribution analysis to trace timestep-level causes of churn probability increases."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "card",
              "subtitle": "Outcome",
              "variant": "timeline",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "With lightweight feature engineering + LightGBM, quickly produced timestep-level churn probabilities and near-real-time interpretation."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "Used interpretation results to evaluate early risk-signal detection and intervention action hypotheses."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
